    <h3>Network Port Scanner</h3>
    <p>Python CLI tool for network reconnaissance. Multi-threaded scanning, port enumeration.</p>
    <div class="tech-stack">Python • Socket Programming • Threading</div>
    <a href="https://github.com/DillanR1/port-scanner">GitHub</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- IT INFRASTRUCTURE LABS -->
<section id="labs" class="portfolio">
  <h2>IT Infrastructure Labs</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">
    Enterprise-grade deployments demonstrating systems administration, virtualization, and automation skills.
    <strong>Built for technical hiring managers and IT recruiters.</strong>
  </p>
  
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Active Directory Domain Deployment</h3>
    <p>Windows Server 2022 forest configuration, PowerShell automation, Hyper-V networking, DNS/DHCP integration.</p>
    <div class="skills-tags">
      <span>Active Directory</span>
      <span>PowerShell</span>
      <span>Hyper-V</span>
      <span>Windows Server</span>
      <span>DNS/DHCP</span>
    </div>
    <a href="/labs/active-directory">View Lab</a>
  </div>
  
  <div class="card">
    <h3>osTicket on Linux (LAMP Stack)</h3>
    <p>Full LAMP deployment: Ubuntu Server, Apache, MySQL, PHP. Database security, web server hardening.</p>
    <div class="skills-tags">
      <span>Linux</span>
      <span>Apache</span>
      <span>MySQL</span>
      <span>PHP</span>
      <span>Security Hardening</span>
    </div>
    <a href="/labs/osticket">View Lab</a>
  </div>
  
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Windows 11 Hyper-V Deployment</h3>
    <p>Generation 2 VM with TPM/Secure Boot, external networking, boot order management, WSL2 conflict resolution.</p>
    <div class="skills-tags">
      <span>Hyper-V</span>
      <span>Windows 11</span>
      <span>Virtualization</span>
      <span>Troubleshooting</span>
    </div>
    <a href="/labs/windows11-vm">View Lab</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CERTIFICATIONS -->
<section class="certs">
  <h2>Certifications & Skills</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>CompTIA A+</strong> — Hardware/Software Troubleshooting, Networking Fundamentals</li>
    <li><strong>In Progress:</strong> CompTIA Network+, Security+</li>
  </ul>
  
  <div class="skills-grid">
    <div class="skill-category">
      <h3>Systems Administration</h3>
      <p>Active Directory, Windows Server, Linux (Ubuntu), Hyper-V, VMware concepts</p>
    </div>
    <div class="skill-category">
      <h3>Scripting & Automation</h3>
      <p>PowerShell, Bash, Python, Infrastructure-as-Code principles</p>
    </div>
    <div class="skill-category">
      <h3>Web Development</h3>
      <p>React, Astro, TypeScript, Node.js, REST APIs, Headless CMS</p>
    </div>
    <div class="skill-category">
      <h3>Networking</h3>
      <p>TCP/IP, DNS, DHCP, Firewall configuration, Virtual switches, Network troubleshooting</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTACT -->
<section class="contact">
  <h2>Let's Build Something</h2>
  <form data-netlify="true" name="contact">
    <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Name" required />
    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" required />
    <textarea name="message" placeholder="Project details or job opportunity..." required></textarea>
    <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
  </form>
</section>

<style>
  /* SKULL WATERMARK */
  .skull-watermark {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: -10%;
    right: -5%;
    width: 400px;
    opacity: 0.08;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: float 20s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  .skull-watermark img {
    width: 100%;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 60px rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.3));
  }
  
  /* STICKY NAV */
  .sticky-nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.3);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    z-index: 1000;
    transform: translateY(-100%);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .sticky-nav.visible {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  
  .nav-logo {
    width: 40px;
    height: auto;
  }
  
  .sticky-nav span {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  /* CTA BUTTONS */
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .cta-primary, .cta-secondary {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .cta-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.3), rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.4));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.5);
    color: #ff6600;
  }
  
  .cta-primary:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.4), rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.5));
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.4);
  }
  
  .cta-secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    color: #fff;
  }
  
  .cta-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  }
  
  /* TECH STACK & SKILLS TAGS */
  .tech-stack, .skills-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  
  .tech-stack {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  .skills-tags span {
    background: rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.3);
    padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    color: #ff8833;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .skills-tags span:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.25);
    border-color: rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.5);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  /* SKILLS GRID */
  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .skill-category {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .skill-category h3 {
    color: #ff6600;
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
  
  .skill-category p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0 0;
  }
  
  /* SECTION INTRO */
  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .section-intro strong {
    color: #ff6600;
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Sticky nav on scroll
  const nav = document.querySelector('.sticky-nav');
  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    if (nav) {
      if (window.scrollY > 200) {
        nav.classList.add('visible');
      } else {
        nav.classList.remove('visible');
      }
    }
  });
</script>